# English UI (Partner Hub)

All **user-facing** text in Partner Hub must be **English**:

- Navigation labels, page titles, form labels, placeholders, buttons, empty states, toasts, errors
- `<select>` / dropdown option text (roles, tiers, statuses, etc.)
- Table headers and badge text shown in the app

Do **not** mix Chinese into the UI (e.g. avoid `Sales (销售)` — use `Sales` only).

**Exceptions** (Chinese is OK):

- User-entered content (partner names, notes, contacts)
- Seed/demo data in research materials outside the app
- Internal code comments (optional; English preferred for consistency)

When adding labels for enums/constants, define English strings in shared maps (e.g. `USER_ROLE_LABELS`) rather than inline Chinese.
